      <title>特朗普媒体的会计师事务所有审计缺陷的历史</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/trump-media-s-accounting-firm-has-history-of-audit-deficiencies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普的社交媒体公司刚刚成为一家会计师事务所最有价值的公开交易客户，该会计师事务所在审计场外交易公司方面拥有更多经验，并且存在一系列监管问题，包括由一家审计机构审查的审计缺陷率为 100%。美国监管机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/trump-media-s-accounting-firm-has-history-of-audit-deficiencies</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 15:01:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院共和党议员敦促指定 TikTok 外国代理人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/tiktok-foreign-agent-designation-pressed-by-key-house-republican</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位众议院共和党高层威胁要传唤司法部，以确定该机构是否正在调查 TikTok 是否违反了要求外国势力代理人向政府登记的美国法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/tiktok-foreign-agent-designation-pressed-by-key-house-republican</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰 Naftogaz 在俄罗斯袭击后向天然气交易商示好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/ukraine-s-naftogaz-courts-gas-traders-after-russian-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管俄罗斯最近对其天然气基础设施发动攻击，乌克兰最大的能源公司仍希望今年与欧洲天然气贸易商达成更多协议，以增加燃料储存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/ukraine-s-naftogaz-courts-gas-traders-after-russian-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 14:52:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国将订购价值高达70亿欧元的舰艇和装甲车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/germany-to-order-ships-armored-vehicles-worth-up-to-7-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国执政联盟将在本季度推进对国家武装部队的全面改革，订购价值高达 70 亿欧元（合 76 亿美元）的两艘海军护卫舰和数百辆装甲运输车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/germany-to-order-ships-armored-vehicles-worth-up-to-7-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 14:37:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非在贸易峰会上抛弃了欧洲一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/south-africa-is-said-to-irk-eu-with-indifference-to-summit-calls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，一年多来，南非未能回应召开高层峰会的要求，使其最大的贸易伙伴和最大的外国投资者欧盟感到沮丧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/south-africa-is-said-to-irk-eu-with-indifference-to-summit-calls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 13:47:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着战争支出飙升，以色列维持利率以保护谢克尔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/israel-holds-rates-to-protect-shekel-and-as-war-spending-soars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加沙战争导致国防支出激增，以色列周一没有降息，央行专注于保护谢克尔并冷却通胀预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/israel-holds-rates-to-protect-shekel-and-as-war-spending-soars</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 13:01:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列官员对与哈马斯的停火谈判表示乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/israel-officials-optimistic-over-talks-with-hamas-on-gaza-hostages-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列高级官员表示，加沙停火谈判已取得进展，其中包括释放人质和巴勒斯坦囚犯，此举引起了极右翼部长的批评，他们威胁要推翻政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/israel-officials-optimistic-over-talks-with-hamas-on-gaza-hostages-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:49:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
